name: TW5FontAwesome
body:
![TW5FontAwesome flag](fa-flag.png)

**TW5FontAwesome** supports embedding [Font Awesome](http://fortawesome.github.io/Font-Awesome/) in [TiddlyWiki 5](http://tiddlywiki.com). There is no need to install this font into your operating system. The font is already embedded in this TiddlyWiki 5 customization instead, so nothing to install at all. Please see the demo for details on how to easily install Font Awesome support into your existing TiddlyWiki 5 instances. It's basically a simple drag&drop operation.
